{"type": "article", "id": 46324, "title": "支付宝找 100 多人拍超长广告，亚马逊开价 50 万美元升级页面 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-10-20T04:41:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 9822, "name": "切尔西"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}, {"id": 2399, "name": "支付宝"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 104, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171020122032QCW0oRbgD2rqUzhJ.png", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 22.0px} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 29.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 19.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #323333} span.s3 {font: 29.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42423\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>麦当劳中国拍了支还不错的音乐广告</b></a>，讲的是和孩子沟通要蹲下来，顺势推介了麦当劳门店的自助点餐机推出的儿童点餐界面。是品牌和产品结合得不错的本土案例，代理公司是琥珀传播。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y0550g6j30h&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42420\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>《时尚芭莎》与万宝龙携手推出的宣传片《拥抱生命印记》</b></a>，桂纶镁、吴敏霞、俞飞鸿分别出演了三支短片，为宝曦系列女士腕表代言。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=o0560oyj7v2&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t<figcaption class=\"\">桂纶镁篇</figcaption></figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=w0559pcm0on&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t<figcaption class=\"\">俞飞鸿篇</figcaption></figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=q0559u6s0pj&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t<figcaption class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23638.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">吴敏霞篇</a></figcaption></figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23638.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Angelababy 和音乐著作人 ZHU 为 adidas Originals 2017 秋冬 SST PURE 系列拍摄了新品大片。</a></b>ZHU 是得到格莱美提名的华裔电子音乐制作人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171020115318xjk7lPteQL3daXiI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563636\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171020115153j4mo5DrTaGbEFU7I.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563636\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171020115258PaS0cGNruQgYUHLV.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563636\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/mgms-first-ad-following-the-las-vegas-shootings-draws-swift-criticism-on-social/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>米高梅重制了他们的品牌宣传大片</b></a>，受到拉斯维加斯枪击案的影响，此前一个版本被临时撤下，但新版本&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" data-sessionlink=\"feature=player-title\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wv4OnUSQjYo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Together We Shine</a>&nbsp;也还是引发了争议，被认为有话题炒作的嫌疑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710201154370rSbn6pDtGgPHuIE.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.421875\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwMTgwMzU2Ng==&amp;mid=2649379123&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=27bd5c32b41606b78431971de6490ec9&amp;chksm=82cae572b5bd6c64482af7e0ef08b584d3e481875fff0556bb5a9bcb2bc509ea4426bb74e1e3&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1019Gq2KgAhaPg2CRbgx2JiX&amp;key=90f7c1bdc0e0328bdd9e4883703e78a020940979494777acaf8c4a93cfb95513924663e3cc6432bcbdfe35cf46776f400a7020d196cad9cd29cd31e9d514cc0279eca2e21e31ef7fb342189822b3a71f&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;pass_ticket=1flqOpMFulV0eOMeKa1c%2B5HyI8yeh6iHbGwMEKCiyHzhJuVj%2BIFK3P%2BBCIpTWaRD\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为了宣传新的 slogan，支付宝拍了一个超长平面广告</b></a>。找了 500 多人进行海选，最后动用了 100 多人拍摄这七个字的广告“支付就用支付宝”。横幅广告太长，<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwMTgwMzU2Ng==&amp;mid=2649379123&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=27bd5c32b41606b78431971de6490ec9&amp;chksm=82cae572b5bd6c64482af7e0ef08b584d3e481875fff0556bb5a9bcb2bc509ea4426bb74e1e3&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1019Gq2KgAhaPg2CRbgx2JiX&amp;key=90f7c1bdc0e0328bdd9e4883703e78a020940979494777acaf8c4a93cfb95513924663e3cc6432bcbdfe35cf46776f400a7020d196cad9cd29cd31e9d514cc0279eca2e21e31ef7fb342189822b3a71f&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;pass_ticket=1flqOpMFulV0eOMeKa1c%2B5HyI8yeh6iHbGwMEKCiyHzhJuVj%2BIFK3P%2BBCIpTWaRD\" rel=\"nofollow\">请戳这里观看</a>。</p><h3>公司又有什么事儿发生</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/disappointing-publicis-results-ricochet-around-ad-industry-1508411856\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>全球第三大广告集团阳狮公布三季度财报，营收下降 6.6%，冲击 WPP 股价也应声下跌 3%。</b></a>阳狮集团表示在 2017 年剩下的时间“难以预测”其业绩。今年 6 月新上任的集团 CEO Arthur Sadoun 此前决定“禁赛一年”，不再参加包括戛纳在内的各类广告节以节省开支，并将公司的业务向更多企业咨询的方面调整。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/digital/twitters-new-service-cranks-out-6-second-videos-for-advertisers/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Twitter 正式推出了 6 秒广告产品</b></a>，名为#Fuel，声称其特点是敏捷、适合快速反映热点的创意。过去几个月里，Twitter 已经在匡威、梅西百货等品牌活动中测试了这种广告形式。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://adage.com/article/digital/amazon-delivers-video-product-pages-brands-pay/310948/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>一直被品牌诟病页面难看，无法传达品牌视觉的亚马逊这次开了个价</b></a>，每年 50 万美元，就可以使用“高级”产品页面服务，果然画面整个就升级了不少的样子。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171020120028xVgCq9yihwNFj8Xd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665109\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.sportsmoney.cn/article/72599.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>索尼音乐和切尔西俱乐部建立独家合作关系</b></a>，官方没有透露合作细节，但发布了一支宣传视频，将足球现场和音乐派对结合在一起，双方可能会在音乐服务中为球迷提供更多粉丝体验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171020120440k2HiJl5QItbSCefR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来源：支付宝</p>"}